<div class="row-fluid">
	<div class="span8">
	{% if is_granted('ROLE_USER') %}
		<h2>Getting Started</h2>
		<p>Need help getting started? If you are new to Arduino and physical programming, take a look at the sample projects we created to get you started or watch our <a href="{{ path('AceStaticBundle_tutorials') }}">tutorials</a>.</p>
		<p>Or you can take a look at various examples on the <a href="{{path("AceGenericBundle_libraries")}}">Examples &amp; Libraries</a> page, and clone a project to your account if you find something interesting.</p>
		<p>If you are already an Arduino user, you can also start by uploading your existing projects online.</p>
	{% else %}
		{% render 'usercontroller:inlineRegisterAction' %}
	{% endif %}
	</div>
	<div class="span4">
		<h2>Donate!</h2>
		<p>Do you like the idea? We need your support. Please consider donating!</p>
		<form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" style="float:right;margin-top: 30px;">
			<input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick">
			<input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="EJCNGL73TNKSG">
			<input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif" style="width:147px;" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!">
			<img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1">
		</form>
	</div>
</div>
